4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program is 16 weeks long, consisting of three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 participants. It covers essential topics such as Windows, Linux, network and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop